    "name": "林山海探案集 - 第一案:仙人跳",
    "steam_appid": 2283690,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283690/extras/1666141c7abaf8d66a0c03a175c790a0.avif?t=1741883578\" width=616 height=196 /></span><strong></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >林山海探案集，是一款依据真实案件改编的3D系列推理解谜探案游戏，美术风格为90年代中式实景风格。作品为系列作品，本案为第一案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283690/extras/6e94bca5811acfef93b78fa3a4344597.avif?t=1741883578\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >案件简介:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有人报案被敲诈2万元，经了解是中了一个俗称“仙人跳”的圈套，但报案人称事情“不那么简单”。到底这个案件背后隐藏着什么令人震惊的真相呢？隐藏多年的惊天连环杀人案由此拉开序幕。睹色相悦人之情，个中原有真缘分。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 搜索线索</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏场景内共有 <strong>40 条线索</strong>，分布在案发现场的各个角落。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要仔细观察，点击或互动场景中的物品，找到隐藏的物证。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些线索可能藏在隐蔽位置，需要仔细探索或使用特殊道具才能发现。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些线索可能需要解谜才能获得</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283690/extras/7f85ac2907fa4ccbc6bd561432d109fb.poster.avif?t=1741883578\" width=750 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283690/extras/7f85ac2907fa4ccbc6bd561432d109fb.webm?t=1741883578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283690/extras/7f85ac2907fa4ccbc6bd561432d109fb.mp4?t=1741883578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 深入分析</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现线索后，玩家可以打开<strong>线索详情</strong>进行阅读，获取更多有价值的信息。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >线索中可能包含物品描述、解谜提示、机关密码等关键内容，帮助玩家梳理案件脉络。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283690/extras/0346d2a7c2bc0bfe6e3cd338cf7028a9.poster.avif?t=1741883578\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283690/extras/0346d2a7c2bc0bfe6e3cd338cf7028a9.webm?t=1741883578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283690/extras/0346d2a7c2bc0bfe6e3cd338cf7028a9.mp4?t=1741883578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 线索关联</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分线索之间存在联系，玩家可以通过<strong>关联系统</strong>进行逻辑推理。(键盘Q进入）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择两条或多条有关联的线索，尝试将它们组合，以推导出<strong>新的隐藏线索</strong>或推理出案件关键信息。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜证足够时，系统会提示玩家，有可关联选项。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. 解开谜团</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过正确推理，推断出案件经过、凶手身份及作案动机，才能成功完成游戏。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真相只有一个！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家Q群</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283690/extras/c48050bc88deac586ca357395dc766b8.avif?t=1741883578\" width=616 height=196 /></span>0号:676614585 <br>1号:606830488 <br>2号:1076610940 <br>3号:736747955</p>",
